{"about_the_game":"You're a dirty scallywag with nothing to lose. Dirty Dirty Pirates is a fast-paced, chaotic, player versus player fighting game, where fast reflexes and improvisation will help you become victorious. Stab, throw, roll, dance, mount, catch, and smash your way through frenzied battles in a looped battleground and enjoy the hilarious brutality.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>LOCAL-MULTIPLAYER MAYHEM</strong></h2>Brawl with 2-8 players in a top down, blood-soaked, pirate battleground not for the faint of heart. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273050/extras/DirtyDirtyPirates_Local_Multiplayer.gif?t=1723566693\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>CHAOTIC LOOPED BATTLEGROUND</strong></h2>You and your thrown weapons wrap around the level, creating chaotic ways to slay your enemies (or yourself)!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273050/extras/DirtyDirtyPirates_Looped_Battleground.gif?t=1723566693\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>POUNCE AND EXECUTE</strong></h2>Mount a downed pirate and choose your killing method. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273050/extras/DirtyDirtyPirates_Mount_Kill.gif?t=1723566693\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>GRATIFYING KILL CAMS</strong></h2>Watch the final kill of the match in slow motion and celebrate the brutality.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273050/extras/DirtyDirtyPirates_Kill_Cam.gif?t=1723566693\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>WEAPONS WITH A MIND OF THEIR OWN</strong></h2><br>Not only are the weapons pointy and eager to impale \u2013 but they follow you! Better hide, catch, or roll, ya buccaneer.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>SLAUGHTER IN DIVERSE LANDS</strong></h2><br>Slay your foes at ship docks, ancient jungle ruins, desert, caves, and icy tundras.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>CUSTOMIZE THE CHAOS</strong></h2><br>Reduce or increase the blood/gore to your liking (or disable it). Color blind mode is available as well. <br><br>Please note: This is a local multiplayer game without online gameplay. For the best experience, find a comfy couch and some friendly mateys in the same room or with Steam Remote Play.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273050/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1723566693","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273050/page.bg.jpg?t=1723566693","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273050/6fdfbeccdf979ec5c3143ef43e1797a99e09be58/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1723566693","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2273050/6fdfbeccdf979ec5c3143ef43e1797a99e09be58/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1723566693","categories":[{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen PvP","id":37},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Remote Play Together","id":44},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"While the blood can be completely disabled, by default you'll see low-poly characters spew high quantities of realistic blood during fights."},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"You're a dirty scallywag with nothing to lose. Dirty Dirty Pirates is a fast-paced, chaotic, player versus player fighting game, where fast reflexes and improvisation will help you become victorious. Stab, throw, roll, dance, mount, catch, and smash your way through frenzied battles in a looped battleground and enjoy the hilarious brutality.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>LOCAL-MULTIPLAYER MAYHEM</strong></h2>Brawl with 2-8 players in a top down, blood-soaked, pirate battleground not for the